\id GAL
\h Galaatiya
\toc3 Gala
\toc2 Galaatiya
\toc1 Phawuloosi Galaatiya Asaas Xaafida Kiitaa
\mt1 Phawuloosi Galaatiya Asaas
\mt2 Xaafida Kiitaa
\imt1 Gaatha Qofaa
\ip Yesuusi ashsheyssa gideyssa odiya Wonggelaa qaalay dumma dumma bessan sabbakettin, Ayhude gidonna asay ammani ammani biya wode, “Kiristtaane gidanaw Muse higge polanaw koshshiyye koshshennee?” yaagiya oyshoy issife denddis. He wode Phawuloosi, “Kiristtaane gidanaw Muse higge polanaw koshshenna; Yesuusan ooratha de7o demmanaw koshshiya waannay, ammano. Asay Xoossaa sinthan xillanaw dandda7ey ammano xalaalan” yaagidi tamaarssis. Shin Guutha Iisiyan, Galaatiya awurajjan de7iya woosa keethan de7iya asaa giddon, “Asi Xoossaa sinthan xillanaw Yesuusa ammano xalaala gidonnashin, Muse higgiyaka polanaw koshshees” yaagidi Phawuloosa timirttiya phalqqiya asati de7oosona.
\ip Phawuloosi Galaatiya maxaafaa xaafiday he balaa timirtten cimettida asaa tuma ammanuwaakkonne ammano de7uwakko zaaranaassa. Phawuloosi Yesuusa hawaare gideyssa tillaydi odo oykkis. Iya hawaare oothidi xeegiday ase gidonnashin Xoossaa gideyssanne I kiitettiday Ayhude gidonna asaas gideyssa qonccisidi odis. Iyara oysethidi asay xillanaw dandda7ey ammano xalaalan gideyssa odees. Wurssetha shemppotan ammano de7oy Yesuusa ammanon benttiya siiqoppe pultteyssa gideyssa odees.
\iot Galaatiya kiitaa ayfe qofata
\io1 Gelo qofaa 1:1-10
\io1 Phawuloosa hawaaretetha maata 1:11-2:21
\io1 Xoossaa aadho keehatethaa Wonggelaa 3:1-4:31
\io1 La77atethinne ammanon duussu 5:1-6:10
\io1 Kuushsha qofaa 6:11-18
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Asappe woykko asa baggara gidonnashin, Yesuus Kiristtoosappenne iya hayqoppe denthida Xoossaa Aawappe hawaare gidana mela kiitettida ta Phawuloosi,
\v 2 taara de7iya ammaniyaa ishati ubbay, Galaatiyan de7iya woosa keethatas kiittida kiitaa.
\p 
\v 3 Xoossay nu Aawaynne nu Godaa Yesuus Kiristtoosi hinttew aadho keehatethaanne sarotethaa immo.
\p 
\v 4 Ha iita wodiyappe nuna ashshanaw, nu Xoossaa, nu Aawa shenen Kiristtoosi nu nagara gisho bana aathi immis.
\v 5 Xoossaas Merinaappe merinaa gakkanaw bonchchoy gido. Amin7i.
\s1 Tuma Wonggelay issino
\p 
\v 6 Kiristtoosa aadho keehatethan hinttena xeegida Xoossaa aggidi, hara Wonggelaakko, hintte ellesidi, waanidi simmidaakko tana malaalisees.
\v 7 Hinttena balethanawunne Kiristtoosa Wonggelaa wobbisanw koyaa guutha asati de7oosonappe attin tuma Wonggelay issino.
\v 8 Shin nuna gidin woykko salo kiitanchcho gidin nuuni hinttew koyro odida Wonggelaappe dummattiya hara Wonggelaa hinttew odiyabaa gidikko, I qanggettidabaa gido.
\v 9 Hayssafe sinthe nuuni gidayssada ha77ika zaarada gays. Hintte ekkida Wonggelaappe dummattiya Wonggelaa oonikka hinttew odikko he uray qanggettidabaa gido.
\p 
\v 10 Yaatin, tana asi nashshana mela koyaynayye? Woykko Xoossi nashshana mela koyaynaa? Woykko ta ase ufayssanaw koyaynaa? Ta ase ufayssanaw koyabaa gidikko, Kiristtoosa aylle gidikke.
\s1 Phawuloosa xeegetethaa
\p 
\v 11 Ta ishato, ta hinttew odida Wonggelay asappe gidonnayssa hintte erana mela ta koyays.
\v 12 Taw ha Wonggelaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosi qonccisisippe attin asappe ekkabiikke woykko asi tana tamaarssibeenna.
\p 
\v 13 Ta kase Ayhude ammanon de7iya wode waana de7idaakko, hintte si7ideta. Ta woosa keethaa qadhey baynna gooddanawnne dhayssanaw baaxetas.\x - \xo 1:13 \xt Ha@O 8:3; 22:4-5; 26:9-11\x*
\v 14 Ayhude ammano naagon, ta woden de7iya Ayhude ishatappe aadhdhays. Nu aawata wogaaskka aadhdhada mishettays.\x - \xo 1:14 \xt Ha@O 22:3\x*
\p 
\v 15 Shin ta buroo ta aaye ulon de7ishin Xoossay tana dooris; ba aadho keehatethan tana xeegis.\x - \xo 1:15-16 \xt Ha@O 9:3-6; 22:6-10; 26:13-18\x*
\v 16 Ayhude gidonna asaas Wonggelaa odana mela Xoossay ba Na7aa taw qonccisida wode ta ooderakka zorettabiikke.
\v 17 Woykko taappe sinthe hawaare gididayssatara gayttanaw Yerusalaame babiikke. Shin ta kasetada Arabe biittaa bas; hessafe simmada Damasqqo katamaa yas.
\v 18 Heedzu laythafe guye, Phexiroosara gayttanaw Yerusalaame bada iyara tammanne ichchashu gallas uttas.\x - \xo 1:18 \xt Ha@O 9:26-30\x*
\v 19 Shin Godaa ishaa Yayqoobappe attin hankko hawaareta be7abiikke.
\p 
\v 20 Ta hinttew xaafiydayssi worddo gidonnayssa Xoossaa sinthan hinttew qonccisays.
\p 
\v 21 Hessafe guye, taani Sooriya biittaanne Kilqiya biittaa bas.
\v 22 Yihudan de7iya woosa keethaa asay tana be7idi eribookkona.
\v 23 Shin entti, “Kase nuna gooddiya uray, ha77i he I dhayssanaw koyaa ammanuwabaa sabbakees” yaageyssa si7idosona.
\v 24 Si7ida ubbay ta gaason Xoossaa galatidosona.
\c 2
\s1 Hawaareti Phawuloosa ekkidosona
\p 
\v 1 Tammanne oyddu laythafe guye, Barnnabaasara zaarada Yerusalaame bas. He wode Tito taara ekkada bas.\x - \xo 2:1 \xt Ha@O 11:30; 15:2\x*
\v 2 Xoossay taw qonccisida qonccethan yaa bada Ayhude gidonna asaa giddon ta sabbakiya Wonggelaa enttaw qonccisas. Kase ta woxxida wothaynne ha77ika ta woxxiya wothay hada gidonna mela gada kaaletheyssata dumma shiishada enttaw odas.
\v 3 Hari attoshin, taara de7iya Titoy Girike asi gidikkoka, qaxxaretto gidi un77ethibookkona.
\v 4 Gidoshin, ammaniyaa ishata daanidi nu giddo gelida issoti issoti I qaxxarettana mela koyidosona. He asati Kiristtoos Yesuusan nuus de7iya la77atethaa wochchidi be7anaw geeman nu giddo gelidi zaaridi nuna aylle oothanaw koyoosona.
\v 5 Shin tuma Wonggelaa hinttenan minnidi daana mela nuuni hari attoshin, guutha wodeskka enttaw kushe immibookko.
\p 
\v 6 Shin halaqa daaniya asata oonatethay taw aykkoka gidenna. Xoossay asa som77o be7idi pirddenna. Ha asati ta markkattiya Wonggelaa bolla gujjidabay baawa.\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Zaare 10:17\x*
\v 7 Shin Phexiroosi, Ayhudetas Wonggelaa odana mela Xoossay iyaw hadara immidayssada tawukka Ayhude gidonna asaas Wonggelaa odiya hadaraa immidayssa entti guyeppe be7idosona.
\v 8 Hiza, Phexiroosi Ayhudeta hawaare gidana mela oothida Xoossay, takka Ayhude gidonna asaas hawaare gidana mela oothis.
\v 9 Qassi tuussu daanidi benttiya Yayqoobi, Phexiroosinne Yohaannisi, taw imettida aadho keehatethaa be7ida wode nuura issifidayssa qonccisanaw ta kushiyanne Barnnabaasa kushiya oykkidosona. Nuuni Ayhude gidonna asaakko, qassi entti Ayhude asaakko baanaw giigidosona.
\v 10 Entti nuna minthidi hadara giday, nuuni manqotas qoppanayssa. Kasekka ta hessa oothanaw amotteys.
\s1 Phawuloosi Phexiroosa timirttiya phalqqis
\p 
\v 11 Phexiroosi Anxookiya katamaa yida wode I balida gisho taani iya som77on “Neeni baladasa” gas.
\v 12 Yayqoobi kiittida guutha asay yaanappe sinthe I Ayhude gidonna asaara mees, shin entti yidaappe guye, “Ayhude gidonna asaappe ammanidayssati qaxxarettanaw bessees” giya asaas yayyidi enttafe shaakettis.
\v 13 Qassi hankko ammanida Ayhudeti Phexiroosa hanuwa Kaallidosona. Hari attoshin, Barnnabaasikka iya qofan gooshettis.
\p 
\v 14 Shin entti Wonggelaa tumatethan suure hamuttonnayssa be7ada, Phexiroosa asa ubbaa sinthan, “Neeni Ayhude gidashe, Ayhude wogaatho gidonnashin, Ayhude gidonna asada de7aasa; yaatin, waanada Ayhude gidonnayssata, ‘Ayhude wogan de7ite gada wolqqatay?’ ” yaagas.
\p 
\v 15 Nuuni yeletan Ayhude, shin nagaranchcho gidida Ayhude gidonna asaa mela gidokko.
\v 16 Shin asi Yesuus Kiristtoosa ammanidi xilleesippe attin higge naagidi xillonnayssa eroos. Oonikka higge naagidi xillonna gisho, nukka higge naagidi gidonnashin, Kiristtoosan ammanidi xillana mela Kiristtoosi Yesuusa ammanida.\x - \xo 2:16 \xt Maz 143:2; Roome 3:20, 22\x*
\p 
\v 17 Nu Ayhudetikka Kiristtoosa baggara xillanaw koshshees. Hessa gidikko nukka hara asada nagaranchcho gideyssa be7oos. Yaatin, nu nagara oothana mela denthethey Kiristtoosa guusseyye? Ubbaka gidenna!
\v 18 Hiza, ta laallidayssa zaarada keexiyabaa gidikko taani ta huu7en higge mentheyssa gideyssa qonccisays.
\v 19 Taani Xoossaas daana mela taani higge baggara higges hayqqas.
\v 20 Taani Kiristtoosara masqaliya bolla kaqettas. Taani hizappe taw de7ikke, shin Kiristtoosi tanan de7ees. Ta ha77i de7iya de7oy, tana dosidi ta gisho bana aathi immida Xoossaa Na7aa ammanada de7ays.
\v 21 Taani Xoossaa aadho keehatethaa hada oothike. Xillotethi asas higge baggara benttiyabaa gidiyakko, Kiristtoosi coo hayqqis guussu.
\c 3
\s1 Xillotethi ammanonna
\p 
\v 1 Hinttenoo, akeeki baynna Galaatiya asato, hintte ayfiyaa sinthan Kiristtoosi masqale bolla kaqettida misileda qonccidi benttees. Yaatin, tumaas hintte kiitettonna mela hinttena bitiday oonee?
\v 2 Ta issibaa eranaw koyays; hintte Geeshsha Ayyaana ekkiday higge naagidiyye woykko hintte si7ida Wonggelaa ammanidi ekkideti?
\v 3 Hintte hessa mela eeye? Hintte Xoossaa Ayyaanan doomidi, ha77i wolqqan polanaw koyeetii?
\v 4 Hintte Wonggelaa gaason daro waayettiday melee? He waaye ubbay coo gididee?
\v 5 Xoossay hinttew Geeshsha Ayyaana immeynne hintte giddon malaatata oothey, hintte higge naagida gishoyye woykko Wonggelaa si7idi ammanida gisho?
\p 
\v 6 Ane Abrahaame be7ite, “I Xoossaa ammanis; Xoossay iyaw hessa xillotethi oothidi ekkis”\x - \xo 3:6 \xt Medhe 15:6; Roome 4:3\x* geetettidi xaafettis.
\v 7 Hiza, ammaneyssati Abrahaame nayta gideyssa erite.\x - \xo 3:7 \xt Roome 4:16\x*
\v 8 Xoossay Ayhude gidonna asaa ammanon xillisanayssa Geeshsha Maxaafay be7idi, “Kawotetha ubbay nenan anjjettana” yaagidi, Wonggelaa Abrahames kasetidi odis.\x - \xo 3:8 \xt Medhe 12:3\x*
\v 9 Hessa gisho, ammaniyaa ubbay ammanida Abrahamera issife anjjettidosona.
\p 
\v 10 Higge naagidi xillana giya oonikka qanggettidayssa. Ays giikko, Geeshsha Maxaafan, “Higge maxaafan xaafettida ubbaa naagonna oonikka qanggettidayssa gido” geetettidi xaafettis.\x - \xo 3:10 \xt Zaare 27:26\x*
\v 11 “Xilloy ammanon daana” geetettidi xaafettida gisho, oonikka Xoossaa sinthan higge naagidi xillonnayssi erettidabaa.\x - \xo 3:11 \xt Ib 2:4\x*
\v 12 Higgey ammanon zemppenna. Shin, “Higgiya naagiya oonikka higgiyan de7on daana” yaagees.\x - \xo 3:12 \xt Leewe 18:5\x*
\p 
\v 13 “Mitha bolla kaqettidi hayqqiya oonikka qanggettidayssa” geetetti xaafettida gisho, Kiristtoosi nu gisho qanggettidayssa gididi, nuna higge qanggethafe wozis.\x - \xo 3:13 \xt Zaare 21:23\x*
\v 14 Xoossay Abrahames immida anjjoy, Yesuus Kiristtoosa baggara Ayhude gidonna asaa gakkana melanne Xoossay immana gida Geeshsha Ayyaana nuuni ammanon ekkana mela hessa oothis.
\s1 Higgenne ufayssa qaalaa
\p 
\v 15 Ta ishato, ta hinttew asa de7on meeze gididi de7iyabaa leemiso oothada odays. Asi caaqqida caaqoy minnidaappe guye, oonikka he caaquwa shaaranaw woykko iya bolla haraa gujjanaw dandda7enna.
\v 16 Xoossay he keeke qaalaa Abrahamesinne iya zerethaas immis. Geeshsha Maxaafay, daro asas odiyada, “Ne zerethatas” geenna. Shin issi asas odiyada, “Ne zerethaas” yaagees; ikka Kiristtoosa.\x - \xo 3:16 \xt Medhe 12:7\x*
\p 
\v 17 Taani gey hayssa; oyddu xeetanne hasttamu laythafe guye imettida higgey, koyro Xoossay minthida caaquwa shaaridi ufayssa qaala dhayssanaw dandda7enna.\x - \xo 3:17 \xt Kessa 12:40\x*
\v 18 Xoossay immiya laatay higgen ekettiyabaa gidiyakko Xoossay immida ufayssaa baggara gideyssi attees. Shin Xoossay ba aadho keehatethan laata Abrahames ufayssa qaala baggara immis.\x - \xo 3:18 \xt Roome 4:14\x*
\p 
\v 19 Yaatin, higgey ays imettidee? Higgey imettiday, Abrahames ufayssa qaali imettida zerethay yaana gakkanaw iita oosoy aybeekko erisanaassa. Higgey kiitanchchota baggara imettidi, gido gididi sigethiya issi asa baggara ooso bolla pee7is.
\v 20 Giddo gididi sigethiya uray issi asa xalaalas gidenna, shin Xoossay issino.
\p 
\v 21 Yaatin, higgey Xoossaa ufayssa qaalara eqettiyye? Akkay, gidenna! Higgey imettiday asas de7o immanaw gidiyakko, xillotethi higge baggara benttanashin.
\v 22 Shin Yesuus Kiristtoosa ammanin benttiya ufayssa qaalay ammaneyssatas imettana mela kumetha alamey nagaras haarettidi de7eyssa Geeshsha Maxaafay odees.
\p 
\v 23 Shin ammanoy yaanappe kase higgey nuna qachchi wothis. He ammanoy qonccana gakkanaw higgey nu bolla gorddi wothis.
\v 24 Hessa gisho, nuuni ammanon xillana mela Kiristtoosi yaana gakkanaw higgey na7a naagiya asa mela nuna naageyssa gidis.
\v 25 Shin ha77i ammanoy yida gisho, higgey hizappe guye na7a naagiya asa mela nuna naageyssi attis.
\p 
\v 26 Hintte ubbay Yesuus Kiristtoosa ammanidi Xoossaa nayta gidideta.
\v 27 Kiristtoosara issino gidanaw xammaqettida ubbay Kiristtoosa ma7oda ma77ideta.
\v 28 Hintte ubbay Kiristtoosan issino gidiya gisho, Ayhude asaa giddoninne Girike asaa giddon, aylle giddoninne womaanno giddon, adde giddoninne maccasa giddon dummatethi baawa.
\v 29 Hiza, hintte Kiristtoosabaa gidikko hintte Abrahaame zare. Xoossaa ufayssa qaalada hintte laatteyssata.\x - \xo 3:29 \xt Roome 4:13\x*
\b
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Ta geyssi hayssa. Laattey na7aa gidi de7ishe, shalo ubbay iyabaa gidikkoka, I ayllefe aykkoka dummatenna.
\v 2 Shin iya aaway gida wodey gakkanaw I hadara ekkidayssata kusheninne naageyssata kushen de7ees.
\v 3 Hessadakka, nuuni na7atethan de7iya wode alamiya wogaas ayllettidi de7ida.
\v 4 Shin wodey gakkida wode Xoossay higgefe garssan, maccasappe yelettida ba na7aa kiittis.
\v 5 I hessa oothiday, higges haarettidi de7eyssata wozanawunne nuna ba nayta oothanaassa.\x - \xo 4:5-7 \xt Roome 8:15-17\x*
\p 
\v 6 Nu Xoossaa nayta gidiya gisho, “Abbaa, Aawaw” gidi xeegiya ba Na7aa Ayyaana nu wozanaa giddo kiittis.
\v 7 Hessa gisho, hizappe neeni Xoossaa na7appe attin aylle gidakka. Neeni iya na7a gidikko, Xoossaa laatteyssa gidadasa.
\s1 Phawuloosi Galaatiya asaas qoppis
\p 
\v 8 Hintte kase Xoossaa eronna wode xoosse gidonnayssatas aylle gididi haarettideta.
\v 9 Shin ha77i hintte Xoossaa erideta; ubbarakka Xoossan erettideta. Yaatin pathonnanne go77onna alame wogatakko guye waanidi simmeetii? Wodhdhi eqqidi, waanidi enttaw aylle gidanaw koyeetii?
\v 10 Dumma gidida gallasata, ageenata, wodetanne laythata hintte loythi bonchcheta.
\v 11 Tana hinttebay yashshees; ta hinttew coo daaburadinaashsha?
\p 
\v 12 Ta ishato, ta hintteda hanida gisho, hintteka taada hanite gada hinttena woossays. Hintte tana aybinkka qohibeekketa.
\v 13 Taani koyro harggettashe hinttew Wonggelaa odidayssa hintte ereeta.
\v 14 Ta harggey hinttew paace gidikkoka, tana saletibekketa; ixxibeeketa. Shin tana Xoossaa kiitanchcho woykko Kiristtoos Yesuusa mokkeyssada mokkideta.
\p 
\v 15 Yaatin, he hinttew de7iya ufayssay ubbay aw bidee? Hinttew dandda7ettidaakko, hintte taw, hintte ayfiyaa kessidi immiyako ixxonnayssa ta markkattays.
\v 16 Yaatin, ta hinttew tuma odida gisho hinttew morkke gidadinaayye?
\p 
\v 17 He asati hinttena banttako zaaranaw koyoosona, shin entta qofay lo77ossa gidenna. Entta qofay hinttena shaakkanaassanne hintte enttaw qoppana mela oothanaassa.
\v 18 Lo77obaa oothanaw amottiko lo77o, shin hessi ta hinttera de7iya wode xalaala gidonnashin ubba wode gido.
\p 
\v 19 Ta siiqo nayto, Kiristtoosi hinttenan misilettana gakkanaw yelos maccasi miixotteyssada ta hintte gisho miixottays.
\v 20 Hinttebay taw haddirssi gidin ta un77ettas; ha77i hintte giddon ta benttada shenetada odiyakko ay mela dosaynashin.
\s1 Aggaaronne Saaro
\p 
\v 21 Muse higgen haarettidi daanaw koyeyssato, ane taw odite; higgey ay giyakko erekketii?
\v 22 Geeshsha Maxaafay, “Abrahames ayllefenne godattefe yelettida nam77u nayti de7oosona” yaagees.\x - \xo 4:22 \xt Medhe 16:15; 21:2\x*
\v 23 Aylle na7ay asi na7a yeliya maaran yelettis, shin godatte na7ay Xoossaa ufayssa qaalan yelettis.
\p 
\v 24 Ha maccasati nam77u caaqotas leemiso gididi ekettoosona. Enttafe issinniya, Siina Deriyappe yidaara, ba nayta aylletethas yelasu; iyakka Aggaaro.
\v 25 Aggaara Arabe biittan de7iya Siina Deriyan leemisettada ha77i de7iya Yerusalaame daanawusu. Ays giikko, iya ba naytara aylletethan de7awusu.
\v 26 Shin salon de7iya Yerusalaamey aylletethan de7ukku; iya nu ubbaas aayo.
\v 27 Geeshsha Maxaafay,
\q1 “Naatte, yelonna maynthete ufaytta;
\q2 naatte miixotta eronnaree ilila.
\q1 Azinara de7iya maccaseeppe,
\q2 azini baynna maccasees nayti daro” yaagees.\x - \xo 4:27 \xt Isa 54:1\x*
\p 
\v 28 Ta ishato, hintte Yisaaqada Xoossaa ufayssa qaalan yelettida nayta.
\v 29 Shin he wode asa maarada yelettidayssi, Ayyaana wolqqan yelettidayssa goodis. Hachchika hessa mela.\x - \xo 4:29 \xt Medhe 21:9\x*
\v 30 Shin Geeshsha Maxaafay woygi? “Aylle na7ay godatte na7aara issife laattonna gisho, aylliw I na7aara wolla kessa yedda” yaagees.\x - \xo 4:30 \xt Medhe 21:10\x*
\v 31 Hessa gisho, ta ishato, nuuni godattee naytappe attin ayllee nayta gidokko.
\c 5
\s1 Kiristtoosan de7iya la77atethaa
\p 
\v 1 Nuuni la77atethan daana mela Kiristtoosi nuna aylletethaafe kessis. Hiza, minnidi eqqite; zaaridi aylletetha qambbaran geloppite.
\p 
\v 2 Ta, Phawuloosi, geyssa si7ite. Hintte qaxxarettanaw koykko, Kiristtoosi hinttena aykkoka maaddenna.
\v 3 Qaxxarettiya oonikka higgey kiittiya ubbaa polanaw besseyssa gujjada ta odays.
\v 4 Higge naagidi xillanaw koyeyssato, Kiristtoosappe shaakettideta; Xoossaa aadho keehatethaafe kunddideta.
\v 5 Shin nuuni Xoossaa Ayyaana baggara ammanon xillanaw ufayssan naagoos.
\v 6 Hiza, Kiristtoos Yesuusan de7ikko, siiqon qoncciya ammanoppe attin qaxxarettin, qaxxarettonna aggin nuna aykkoka maaddenna.
\p 
\v 7 Kase hintte lo77o woxxeeta, shin ha77i tumaas kiitettonna mela hinttena diggiday oonee?
\v 8 Hayssa mela iita cimoy hinttena xeegida Xoossaafe yibeenna.
\v 9 Hessika, “Guutha irshshoy munuqa ubbaa denthees.”\x - \xo 5:9 \xt 1Qoro 5:6\x* geetettidi xaafettidayssa mela.
\v 10 Hinttew hara qofi baynnayssas ta Godan ammanettays. Shin hinttena buqiya oonikka Xoossafe ba pirddaa ekkana.
\p 
\v 11 Ta ishato, ta ha77i gakkanaw qaxxaro sabbakkiyabaa gidikko, yaatin tana ays gooddonaa? Hessi tuma gidiyakko Kiristtoosa masqaliyabaa tamaarssoy asaas dhube gidennashin.
\v 12 Hinttena buqeyssati qaxxaretetha xalaala gidonnashin, banttana qaaratiyakkoka ta dosays.
\p 
\v 13 Ta ishato, hintte la77a daanaw xeegettideta. Gidoshin, hintte la77atethay asho amo polanaw hinttew gaaso gidoppo; hessafe aathidi issoy issuwa siiqon maaddite.
\v 14 Higge ubbay, “Ase needa dosa” yaagiya issi qaalan qashettis.\x - \xo 5:14 \xt Leewe 19:18\x*
\v 15 Shin hintte issoy issuwara saxetiyabaanne meetettiyabaa gidikko, hintte woli wurssonna mela naagettite.
\s1 Ayyaana de7onne asho de7o
\p 
\v 16 Hiza, ta hinttew odays; Ayyaanan de7ite; hintte asho amuwaa poloppite.
\v 17 Asho amoy Ayyaana amuwaara morkke; qassi Ayyaana amoykka asho amuwaara morkke. Entti issoy issuwara ixettiya gisho hintte dosiyabaa oothanaw dandda7ekketa.\x - \xo 5:17 \xt Roome 7:15-23\x*
\v 18 Shin Ayyaanay hinttena kaalethiyabaa gidikko higgey hinttena haarenna.
\p 
\v 19 Asho oosoti erettidayssata; enttika, laymatethi, tunatethi, qayxe,
\v 20 eeqa goynno, bita, morkketethi, kachchi, qanaate, hanqo, bana doso, shaaketethi, iita tobbe
\v 21 gene, matho, yethinne hessa hessa melata. Kase ta hinttew odidayssada ha77ika ta hinttew odays. Hayssa melabata ootheyssati Xoossaa kawotethaa laattokona.
\p 
\v 22 Shin Ayyaana ayfey, siiqo, ufayssi, sarotethi, dandda7a, keehatethi, lo77otethi, ammano,
\v 23 ashkketethi, bana haaro. Hayssa melabata ixxiya higgey baawa.
\p 
\v 24 Kiristtoos Yesuusabaa gididayssati bantta ashuwa iya iita qofaranne iya amuwaara issife masqaliya bolla kaqqidosona.
\v 25 Nu Ayyaanan de7iyabaa gidikko, nuna Ayyaanay kaaletho.
\v 26 Ane issoy issuwa yiloyishenne qanaatishe coo ceeqetteyssa aggoos.
\c 6
\s1 Issoy issuwa maaddite
\p 
\v 1 Ta ishato, issi asi nagaran kunddiko, Ayyaanan de7iya hintte he uraa ashkketethan suurisite. Shin neeni hessa melaban paacettonna mela nena naaga.
\v 2 Issoy issuwa deexo toohuwa tookkite. Yaatikko Kiristtoosa higgiya poleeta.
\v 3 Issi asi aykkoyka baawashin, bana haratappe lo77o gidi qoppiko, I bana cimmees.
\v 4 Shin issi issi asi ba oosuwa paacco. Hessafe guye, haratara bana gaaddeyeyssa aggidi baw ceeqettiyabaa demmees.
\v 5 Issi issi asi ba toohuwa baw tookkanaw bessees.
\p 
\v 6 Xoossaa qaala tamaariya oonikka lo77obaa ubbaa ba asttamaariyara shaakettees.
\p 
\v 7 Hinttee, hinttena cimmofite. Asi ba zeridabaa zaaridi cakkiya gisho Xoossaa bolla qelqisoppite.
\v 8 Ba asho amuwaa kunthanaw zeriya oonikka, ba asho amuwaappe hayqo buuccana. Shin Ayyaanaa ufayssanaw zeriya oonikka Ayyaanaappe merinaa de7o cakkana.
\v 9 Ane lo77o ooso oothanaw azalleyssa aggoos. Nuuni azallonna ixxiko wodey gakkiya wode nu zeridayssa cakkana.
\v 10 Nu injje wode demmiko, asa ubbaas, aathidikka ammaniyaa asaas lo77obaa oothoos.
\s1 Wurssetha zorenne sarotaa
\p 
\v 11 Taani ta kushen, ay mela gita pidaalen hinttew xaafidaakko be7ite.
\v 12 Asa sinthan lo77o gididi benttanaw koyaa asati hintte qaxxarettana mela koyoosona. Shin hessa entti oothey, Kiristtoosa masqaliya gisho enttana goodi gakkonna melassa.
\v 13 Entti hintte qaxxaretethan ceeqettanaw koyidi hinttena qaxxaretto goosonappe attin qaxxarettidayssatikka bantta huu7en higgiya naagokkona.
\p 
\v 14 Shin alamey taw kaqettidayssafenne taanikka alamiyas kaqettida, Godaa Yesuus Kiristtoosa masqaliyappe attin hara ceeqetethi taappe haakko.
\v 15 Hiza, qaxxarettin qaxxarettonna aggin aykkoka maaddenna. Maaddey ooratha medhetethi gido.
\v 16 Ha wogaa kaalliya ubbaasinne Xoossaa dere gidida Isra7eeles sarotethaynne maarotethay gido.
\p 
\v 17 Taani Yesuusas madunxida beeta ta asatethan tookkida gisho, hizappe tana oonikka waaysoppo.
\p 
\v 18 Ta ishato, nu Godaa Yesuus Kiristtoosa aadho keehatethay hinttera gido. Amin7i. 
